The <code>AllowBatchCraft</code> parameter is used to allow the recipe to be crafted in batches. This will make a slider appear on the crafting to craft multiple ones at once. Needs to be a boolean and default is <code>true</code>, set to <code>false</code> to disable batch craft.

==Example==
{{CodeSnip
| lang = lua
| code =
AllowBatchCraft = false,
}}
